</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="30.[143,759,609,692]" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">
<emphasis box="[143,268,609,630]" italics="true" pageId="30" pageNumber="31">Etymology.</emphasis>
Named after Dr Paul Hanson, whose Malaise trapping programme has collected many new phorid flies.
</paragraph>
